Package org.apache.ignite.internal.igfs.common

Contains IGFS classes that are common between client and server.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IgfsControlResponse
    IGFS path command response.
    IgfsDataInputStream
    Data input stream implementing object input but throwing exceptions on object methods.
    IgfsDataOutputStream
    Data output stream implementing ObjectOutput but throwing exceptions on methods working with objects.
    IgfsHandshakeRequest
    Handshake request.
    IgfsLogger
    IGFS client logger writing data to the file.
    IgfsMarshaller
    Implementation of IGFS client message marshaller.
    IgfsMessage
    Abstract class for all messages sent between IGFS client (Hadoop File System implementation) and IGFS server (Ignite data node).
    IgfsModeResolverRequest
    Handshake request.
    IgfsPathControlRequest
    Single path command message.
    IgfsStatusRequest
    IGFS status (total/used/free space) request.
    IgfsStreamControlRequest
    Read block request.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IgfsIpcCommand
    Grid file system commands to call remotely.
